rs that correspond to the labels. If not provided, the labels will default to white."},"308":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-19","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#label-options","content":"A donut chart with labels and label colors"},"309":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-20","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"Or you can use the `dataLabels` option to show the data values instead of custom labels:"},"310":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-21","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"A donut chart with data labels"},"311":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-22","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"The `dataLabels` option also accept `\"percentage\"`:"},"312":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-23","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#data-labels","content":"A donut chart with percentage data labels"},"313":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-24","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"The `centerLabel` option allows you to place a label in the center of the donut chart, which can be used to show a title or other value."},"314":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-25","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"A donut chart with a center label"},"315":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-26","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"If you set the `centerLabel` option to `\"sum\"` the center label will show the sum of the data values:"},"316":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-27","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"A donut chart with the sum of the data values as the center label"},"317":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-28","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"**Adjusting center label styles**"},"318":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-29","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"There are a couple options that allow for adjustment of common title text styles for the center label."},"319":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-30","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontSize`"},"320":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-31","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `32`"},"321":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-32","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontWeight`"},"322":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-33","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"defaults to `bold`"},"323":{"id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples-34","page_id":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/docs/examples/donutchart-examples#center-label","content":"`centerLabelFontFamily`"},"